(BOTH GRUNTING)

02:32.569 --> 02:33.779
(SHOUTS)

02:33.862 --> 02:35.030
(GAGGING)

02:35.113 --> 02:36.615
(YELLS)

02:37.324 --> 02:38.367
(GASPS)

02:40.953 --> 02:41.954
(COUGHING)

