you little piece of shit.

05:44.636 --> 05:47.764
-Will you please just let me talk to him?
-Huh? Huh?

05:48.390 --> 05:49.766
KAI: Scooter, let him through.

06:03.655 --> 06:05.490
Take a seat, son.

06:10.871 --> 06:12.414
Thank you, Divine Ruler.

06:12.497 --> 06:14.374
-My name is...
-Trevor Geary.

06:14.458 --> 06:17.169
Age 19, serving 25 years.

06:17.836 --> 06:20.631
-Am I right?
-How do you know that?

06:21.215 --> 06:23.550
I'm not a strong man, Trevor.

06:23.634 --> 06:25.802
