to the monsters in this place.

06:25.886 --> 06:28.555
I realized my first month
that if I wanted to survive,

06:28.639 --> 06:33.101
I had to make it my business to
know everything about everyone.

06:33.727 --> 06:37.898
Eleven months later,
my movement is 16 men strong.

06:39.650 --> 06:41.568
Raise your pinky.

06:47.783 --> 06:49.493
We're connected now, Trevor.

06:49.576 --> 06:52.913
Obligated to tell the truth,
the whole truth and nothing but.

06:53.121 --> 06:55.165
Like being under oath.

06:56.208 --> 06:57.709
Got it?

06:58.126 --> 06:59.586
Yeah.

07:01.463 --> 07:03.757
-You need protection.
-Yes.

07:05.092 --> 07:07.427
I get the shit kicked out of me every day.

07:08.053 --> 07:09.888
I've only been here a month.

07:09.972 --> 07:12.307
-I'm gonna die here unless...
-You're a coward.

07:14.059 --> 07:15.185
What?

07:15.269 --> 07:17.604
