07:34.246 --> 07:36.915
But I'll do anything
to join your gang.

07:36.999 --> 07:38.333
This isn't a gang.

07:38.417 --> 07:39.751
It's an army.

07:39.835 --> 07:41.170
These are my soldiers,

07:41.253 --> 07:43.547
and this place is
a fertile breeding ground.

07:43.630 --> 07:45.507
While women destroy
the world outside,

07:45.591 --> 07:47.926
we wait safely
for our time to strike.

07:48.135 --> 07:50.220
Whatever, man. I'm just...

07:50.429 --> 07:52.639
I'm just so scared.

07:52.764 --> 07:54.892
Do you swear
to devote yourself fully

07:54.975 --> 07:57.394
to me and my cause,

07:57.477 --> 07:59.688
and to never question me?

07:59.771 --> 08:01.231
Yes.

08:01.690 --> 08:03.901
-I fucking swear it.
-Good.

08:04.943 --> 08:06.361
We will protect you

08:06.445 --> 08:08.488
