08:11.950 --> 08:14.786
-(TREVOR SIGHS)
-(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

08:18.916 --> 08:20.292
(SIGHS)

08:20.751 --> 08:23.337
How the hell did a man
like you end up here?

08:24.546 --> 08:26.298
Same as any of these guys.

08:27.090 --> 08:30.219
I was sold out by a filthy...

08:31.136 --> 08:33.764
fucking... rat.

08:34.223 --> 08:36.141
(LINE RINGING)

08:36.225 --> 08:38.185
