08:38.268 --> 08:39.853
Where the fuck is he?

08:39.937 --> 08:40.938
Hey.

08:41.021 --> 08:42.314
Speedwagon hasn't missed
a single gathering,

08:42.397 --> 08:43.857
and he's never even been late.

08:44.316 --> 08:45.359
Get off the phone.

08:45.442 --> 08:47.611
Fuck, I don't have time for this shit.
There's too much to do.

08:47.694 --> 08:49.363
-Open up.
-We got to get started.

08:49.446 --> 08:50.822
They're waiting for you.

08:50.906 --> 08:53.659
(KAI INHALES AND EXHALES DEEPLY)

08:53.742 --> 08:55.285
Give me that.

09:00.958 --> 09:02.543
Okay.

09:03.168 --> 09:04.795
A little bad news to start.

09:06.588 --> 09:09.466
It turns out finding
1,000 pregnant women to murder...

09:09.550 --> 09:11.093
super hard.

09:11.552 --> 09:14.263
No one will ever accuse me
of lacking ambition.

09:15.848 --> 09:17.307
So...

09:17.391 --> 09:19.351
Night of a Thousand Tates is off.

09:19.434 --> 09:20.686
(MEN SIGH)

09:21.186 --> 09:25.023
But... Night of One Hundred Tates is on.

09:25.107 --> 09:26.900
MEN: Yes!

09:27.484 --> 09:29.736
Look under your chairs.
Ally's handed each of you

09:29.820 --> 09:32.656
