all ready to pop.

09:34.950 --> 09:37.035
You raise your hand
one more fucking time,

09:37.119 --> 09:38.829
and I will cut it off.

09:38.912 --> 09:41.206
How do we know
they're all pregnant?

09:41.832 --> 09:44.918
Because Gutterball pulled
the rosters of four ob-gyns,

09:45.002 --> 09:47.963
two Lamaze classes
and a Momtra Yoga over on Main.

09:48.046 --> 09:50.299
Great job, Gutterball.

09:51.425 --> 09:54.928
Manson's family... I admire 'em,

09:55.012 --> 09:57.097
but they did get
a little sloppy.

09:57.639 --> 09:59.725
Their message got lost
in their mess.

09:59.892 --> 10:02.686
What we are doing requires
more precision.

10:02.769 --> 10:05.898
It is imperative that both
mother and child are impaled.

10:06.231 --> 10:07.816
Don't fuck this up!

10:09.359 --> 10:11.862
