10:36.678 --> 10:39.181
They can't ignore
an injustice this brutal.

10:39.264 --> 10:41.934
They'll have to rise up,
and in their collective rage,

10:42.017 --> 10:44.102
they will train it
on Senator Jackson,

10:44.186 --> 10:45.938
on all incumbents,

10:46.021 --> 10:48.857
on any of the people in power
who failed to keep us safe.

10:48.941 --> 10:51.026
