11:57.384 --> 12:01.180
I wanted to be the last person alive.

12:03.182 --> 12:04.600
But...

12:05.100 --> 12:06.852
I just want to die.

12:08.729 --> 12:10.063
Now.

12:12.107 --> 12:13.692
Kill me.

12:14.359 --> 12:16.612
Ally, please.

12:17.362 --> 12:19.615
I'm begging you.

12:23.285 --> 12:26.163
I helped ruin your life.

12:28.916 --> 12:30.959
