12:54.191 --> 12:56.485
What's happening tomorrow night

12:58.028 --> 13:00.697
will be glorious.

13:00.781 --> 13:02.282
You'll see.

13:06.078 --> 13:08.580
I know it's hard
when you've lost your faith

13:08.664 --> 13:10.207
to find it again.

13:10.916 --> 13:13.043
Believe me, I know.

13:13.919 --> 13:16.755
