a little while longer.

13:18.006 --> 13:19.758
KAI: Where the hell are you, Speedwagon?

13:19.842 --> 13:20.968
I'm freaking out, man.

13:21.051 --> 13:23.679
Call me back
as soon as you get this. Fuck.

13:23.762 --> 13:26.348
