for two days?

14:22.696 --> 14:24.114
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

14:24.198 --> 14:26.074
I was afraid, Kai.

14:26.366 --> 14:27.993
Afraid of what?

14:29.328 --> 14:31.038
Afraid of what, Ally?

14:31.121 --> 14:33.999
I was afraid what happened
would break your heart.

14:34.458 --> 14:36.627
ALLY:
<i>Hello, Speedwagon.</i>

14:37.544 --> 14:39.296
