not a transmitter.

15:40.315 --> 15:41.859
Okay, good.

15:43.068 --> 15:44.486
(LOUD, RASPY BREATHING)

15:44.570 --> 15:46.071
Shh. Take a deep breath.

15:46.154 --> 15:48.407
-Okay.
-It's gonna be okay.

15:49.658 --> 15:51.159
(GROANS)

15:51.743 --> 15:53.287
ALLY: Winter was innocent.

15:53.495 --> 15:55.163
