16:09.428 --> 16:11.138
He fooled us all.

16:14.558 --> 16:16.351
(KAI SIGHS)

16:24.443 --> 16:26.987
(KAI GROANS)

16:27.237 --> 16:28.780
Fu...

16:28.864 --> 16:31.950
(CRYING) Oh, God!

16:32.034 --> 16:34.077
(SOBBING)

16:34.161 --> 16:35.579
Shh. Shh, shh.

16:35.662 --> 16:37.748
What have I done?

16:39.333 --> 16:40.918
Oh...

16:41.001 --> 16:43.212
I'm so sorry.

16:43.295 --> 16:44.963
It's okay.

16:45.047 --> 16:47.341
I killed her.
I killed her over nothing.

16:47.424 --> 16:49.718
(KAI SNIFFLES)

16:50.010 --> 16:51.553
You listen to me.

16:51.637 --> 16:53.931
-You can give her death meaning.
-(CRIES)

16:54.014 --> 16:56.475
You can channel this rage,

16:56.558 --> 16:58.602
become the leader
she wanted you to be.

16:58.685 --> 17:00.729
Be the man that she believed in.

17:01.021 --> 17:04.024
You can finish
what you both started.

17:04.107 --> 17:05.442
(KAI SNIFFLES)

17:05.526 --> 17:09.446
You carry out your plan tomorrow night,

17:10.322 --> 17:13.742
and you smack this country
out of its desiccated stupor

17:13.825 --> 17:16.453
and build the world
you wanted for <i>her.</i>

17:17.329 --> 17:19.289
For all of us.

17:20.666 --> 17:23.168
You can do it.
I know you can.

17:24.878 --> 17:27.548
Tonight is the night.

17:29.132 --> 17:30.843
Open your backpacks.

17:32.094 --> 17:34.346
We're going
to assemble your kill kits.

17:35.097 --> 17:36.181
Ka-Bar.

17:36.265 --> 17:38.100
-ALL: Check!
-A change of clothes.

17:38.183 --> 17:39.935
Bring your bloody clothes
back with you to be burned

17:40.018 --> 17:42.229
-in the victory bonfire.
-ALL: Check!

17:42.312 --> 17:43.981
Chloroform and a rag
to soak it in.

17:44.064 --> 17:45.440
