17:45.524 --> 17:46.733
for you guys dealing
with multiple targets

17:46.817 --> 17:48.777
-like the Lamaze class.
-ALL: Check!

17:49.361 --> 17:50.821
What about their husbands?

17:50.904 --> 17:53.532
Shock and awe.
They die first.

17:53.615 --> 17:54.825
ALL:
Check!

17:55.534 --> 17:56.743
KAI:
Listen to me.

17:56.952 --> 17:58.328
The most important thing

17:58.412 --> 17:59.746
is not in the kill kit.

18:00.998 --> 18:02.708
It's inside you.

18:03.625 --> 18:05.669
Are you able and willing

18:05.752 --> 18:08.255
-to die for our cause?
-ALL: Check!

18:08.338 --> 18:10.465
Are you ready to make history?

18:10.549 --> 18:11.633
Yeah!

18:14.094 --> 18:16.930
Hoorah! Divine Ruler!
Hoorah! Divine Ruler!

18:17.014 --> 18:19.433
Hoorah! Divine Ruler!
Hoorah! Divine Ruler...

18:19.683 --> 18:22.853
(CHANTING CONTINUES)

18:25.314 --> 18:27.774
Fortify yourselves
with some vitamin A!

18:27.858 --> 18:30.736
(CHEERING)

18:43.081 --> 18:44.583
Where are you going?

18:45.751 --> 18:47.794
