to get some snacks.

19:02.267 --> 19:03.977
Go. Go now!

19:04.061 --> 19:06.063
AGENT:
We're on, we're on.

19:07.356 --> 19:08.649
Go, go.

19:08.732 --> 19:10.317
SANDSTORM: I don't get this map shit.

19:10.400 --> 19:11.944
Can I just put the address
in my phone?

19:12.027 --> 19:14.196
KAI: Yes, Sandstorm.
Get there any way you know how.

19:14.279 --> 19:16.782
Divine Ruler,
did you send Ally...

19:16.865 --> 19:18.659
FBI. You're under arrest.

19:20.285 --> 19:22.329
Motherfucker.

19:22.412 --> 19:24.331
(EXPLOSIONS)

19:25.457 --> 19:28.252
(MUTED SHOUTING)

19:40.389 --> 19:42.015
(GUNFIRE)

19:45.894 --> 19:47.896
(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)

20:01.326 --> 20:02.661
(GUNSHOT)

20:17.384 --> 20:18.468
(GUNSHOT)

20:22.055 --> 20:23.390
No!

20:39.656 --> 20:42.659
You were right, Ally.
I just had to hang on.

20:52.211 --> 20:53.212
Rat!

20:53.629 --> 20:54.922
You bitch!

20:55.005 --> 20:57.591
I'll fucking kill you!

20:59.092 --> 21:00.302
Ah...

21:02.095 --> 21:05.057
You bitch!
You fucking bitch!

21:05.349 --> 21:07.768
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

21:14.608 --> 21:16.068
Hello, guys. How are you?

21:16.151 --> 21:17.736
-Everything to your satisfaction?
-Oh, yes.

21:17.819 --> 21:19.404
-Our meals are perfect.
-Wonderful.

21:19.488 --> 21:21.031
Better than ever.

21:22.824 --> 21:24.243
I hate to impose,

21:24.326 --> 21:26.370
a-and I'm sure you get this
every day, but...

21:26.453 --> 21:28.705
can I take a picture with you?

21:28.789 --> 21:30.499
I read about what
you had to go through,

21:30.582 --> 21:32.376
escaping from that cult.

21:32.459 --> 21:35.963
I think you're one of the most inspiring
women of our time.

21:36.547 --> 21:39.007
Well, that is very flattering.
Thank you.

21:39.091 --> 21:41.760
I only wish it were true.

21:41.844 --> 21:44.096
You know, I'd really rather not
take that picture.

21:44.179 --> 21:46.390
I'm just... I'm trying to put
all that behind me.

21:46.473 --> 21:48.058
Oh, of course.

21:48.141 --> 21:49.226
But thank you so much
for coming in,

21:49.309 --> 21:50.811
and I hope you enjoy your food.

21:52.521 --> 21:54.398
ALLY: Hello...

21:55.357 --> 21:56.775
Just one.

21:56.859 --> 22:00.320
I'm sorry, we're completely
booked for the evening.

22:00.654 --> 22:02.030
Ally.

22:03.532 --> 22:05.951
What's a girl got to do
to get a table around here?

22:13.834 --> 22:15.335
You must have heard.

22:15.419 --> 22:18.672
Kai pled guilty to everything.

22:18.755 --> 22:20.465
He's not going to trial.

22:21.466 --> 22:23.218
That doesn't surprise you?

22:25.721 --> 22:27.139
Why do you care?

22:27.222 --> 22:29.516
Because I'm waiting for
the other shoe to drop.

22:29.600 --> 22:31.476
Why didn't he turn me in?

22:31.560 --> 22:34.897
They took me in the night of the raid,
then let me go.

22:34.980 --> 22:37.274
Not another word since.

22:37.357 --> 22:39.276
Beverly, you didn't fit the profile.

22:39.359 --> 22:43.322
A black woman in a cult
of angry white nationalists?

22:43.405 --> 22:45.115
They thought you were
an unwilling victim.

22:45.199 --> 22:46.575
You were the informant.

22:46.658 --> 22:48.202
Is that what you told them?

22:48.285 --> 22:50.078
I told them the truth.

22:50.871 --> 22:54.082
I didn't see that you were
involved in any crime,

22:55.125 --> 22:56.919
except being subservient

22:57.002 --> 22:59.713
to those misogynistic assholes.

23:00.214 --> 23:01.757
That still doesn't explain

23:01.840 --> 23:04.051
what Kai did or didn't do.

23:04.134 --> 23:06.011
The DA offered a plea.

23:07.721 --> 23:11.308
He waives a trial to save himself
from the death penalty.

23:12.100 --> 23:14.561
He's such a narcissist,
he couldn't bear to have

23:14.645 --> 23:15.938
anyone else take credit.

23:16.021 --> 23:17.981
You got to admit
it's driving you crazy,

23:18.065 --> 23:20.108
waiting for him
to turn on you.

23:20.567 --> 23:23.529
How did you get so lucky to come
out smelling like a rose?

23:27.157 --> 23:29.409
ALLY: <i>The FBI came to see me</i>

23:29.493 --> 23:31.870
<i>when Vincent put me</i>
<i>in the psychiatric ward.</i>

23:31.954 --> 23:34.248
<i>They had their suspicions</i>
<i>about Kai back then,</i>

23:34.331 --> 23:36.041
<i>after the assassination attempt.</i>

23:36.124 --> 23:38.043
BEVERLY: <i>And that's when</i>
<i>you joined the cult.</i>

23:38.126 --> 23:41.338
I became invaluable to the FBI,

23:41.421 --> 23:43.549
and in return,
I got immunity.

23:44.883 --> 23:46.343
Damn, Ally.

23:46.426 --> 23:48.428
You're the one
they all should be afraid of.

23:48.512 --> 23:49.721
Ha!

23:49.805 --> 23:51.473
Of all the pain you endured,

23:52.182 --> 23:56.478
I'm sure watching Kai kill Ivy
right in front of you

23:56.562 --> 23:58.939
must have been
the most difficult.

24:01.733 --> 24:03.485
It was.

24:05.779 --> 24:08.782
I couldn't process it
for a long time.

24:09.283 --> 24:12.369
Obviously, I still haven't.

24:13.537 --> 24:16.123
Her last words to me were:

24:16.206 --> 24:17.457
"I love you.

24:17.541 --> 24:19.251
"I'm sorry.

24:20.669 --> 24:22.671
"Protect our son."

24:25.299 --> 24:26.758
So I did.

24:27.759 --> 24:30.429
You do know that Kai took credit

24:30.512 --> 24:32.681
for every murder

24:32.764 --> 24:34.850
except Ivy's.

24:34.933 --> 24:37.227
He says you did that.

24:37.311 --> 24:40.564
For revenge
for all that she had taken from you.

24:40.647 --> 24:42.816
Yeah, I-I think I read that...

24:42.900 --> 24:44.735
in <i>The New York Times.</i>

24:44.818 --> 24:46.612
It's absurd, right?

24:47.821 --> 24:50.324
Yes. Absurd.

24:51.783 --> 24:53.827
I joined his cult to save Oz,

24:53.911 --> 24:56.330
to <i>save </i>Ivy.

24:58.916 --> 25:00.959
But I couldn't save them both.

25:03.420 --> 25:05.422
I could only save one.

25:08.008 --> 25:09.259
I believe you.

25:09.343 --> 25:11.053
(EXHALES) Thank you.

25:13.347 --> 25:14.890
I know a lot of women, though,

25:14.973 --> 25:17.434
who would kill their spouse

25:17.518 --> 25:21.230
if they were that betrayed,
that humiliated.

25:22.147 --> 25:24.233
And I bet every woman
in the world

25:24.316 --> 25:26.568
would understand that reaction.

25:33.242 --> 25:35.494
How have you been holding up?

25:38.997 --> 25:41.124
I went from a TV news reporter

25:41.208 --> 25:43.210
to tending bar
at The Flaming Lips.

25:43.293 --> 25:44.837
It's not so bad.

25:44.920 --> 25:47.297
Compliments of the house.

25:47.381 --> 25:48.423
Thank you.

25:48.507 --> 25:50.008
Pardon my reach.

25:51.301 --> 25:52.803
Beverly,

25:53.470 --> 25:55.472
this is my girlfriend

25:55.556 --> 25:58.559
of eight weeks and two days... Erika.

25:58.642 --> 26:01.228
-Nice to meet you.
-Nice to meet you.

26:01.311 --> 26:03.647
We need to finalize
Oz's birthday party.

26:03.730 --> 26:05.440
I know. Um...

26:06.108 --> 26:07.776
It's Saturday.

26:07.860 --> 26:11.405
I'm leaning towards mint green
tea cake, in honor of Ivy.

26:11.613 --> 26:14.074
-You want to come?
-I'd love to.

26:14.658 --> 26:16.451
-Another plus one.
-(ALLY, ERIKA CHUCKLE)

26:18.829 --> 26:21.582
-You okay?
-Mmm-hmm. Yeah. I'm okay.

26:25.377 --> 26:27.796
Dating again. I'm impressed.

26:27.880 --> 26:29.965
Yeah, I know.
I'm supposed to be

26:31.008 --> 26:35.137
"a nice little girl in mourning
for the rest of her life."

26:35.512 --> 26:37.264
Well, fuck that.

26:38.724 --> 26:40.184
I'm living.

26:42.227 --> 26:43.729
Are you ready?

26:44.688 --> 26:46.398
Make a wish.

26:50.944 --> 26:53.530
-(WHOOPS)
-(CHEERS AND APPLAUSE)

26:53.614 --> 26:55.407
Hey, what'd you wish for, kiddo?

26:55.490 --> 26:56.658
-(MOUTHS)
-If I tell you, it won't come true.

26:56.742 --> 26:58.452
That's a good answer.

26:58.535 --> 26:59.745
I was testing you there.

26:59.828 --> 27:00.996
Okay, help yourselves, everyone.

27:01.079 --> 27:02.080
I'll get you plates.

27:02.164 --> 27:03.207
Ooh, this looks good.

27:03.290 --> 27:04.791
(PHONE RINGS)

27:04.875 --> 27:07.211
-Want me to get that?
-Yes, thank you.

27:07.294 --> 27:08.462
Here you go.

27:08.545 --> 27:10.214
Hello?

27:11.215 --> 27:12.549
(STAMMERS)

27:12.633 --> 27:14.218
She's not gonna do it.

27:20.390 --> 27:21.767
Rachel Maddow's people again.

27:21.850 --> 27:22.851
Jesus, she's still at it?

27:22.935 --> 27:24.770
Yeah. I already said no. Twice.

27:24.853 --> 27:26.355
I told them that again.

27:28.357 --> 27:30.150
Maybe it's not the worst thing
in the world

27:30.234 --> 27:31.610
if you did
one of these interviews.

27:31.693 --> 27:33.028
No, I don't want to.

27:33.111 --> 27:35.239
She is a legit feminist icon.

27:35.322 --> 27:36.782
Tell her, please.

27:36.865 --> 27:38.283
If she turned down Lana Winters,

27:38.367 --> 27:39.743
why would she talk to
Rachel fucking Maddow?

27:39.826 --> 27:41.245
Thank you. And besides,

27:41.328 --> 27:42.871
all I'm trying to do is
put this behind me.

27:42.955 --> 27:45.749
I never wanted to be an icon.
All I want to do is

27:45.832 --> 27:48.168
be a soccer mom
and a small business owner.

27:48.252 --> 27:50.087
-(PHONE RINGING)
-I will get it.

27:50.170 --> 27:51.713
-Okay.
-Thank you, but I'll get it.

27:54.758 --> 27:55.801
Hello?

27:55.884 --> 27:56.969
OPERATOR:
<i>This is a collect call from...</i>

27:57.344 --> 27:58.762
KAI: <i>Kai Anderson.</i>

27:58.846 --> 28:02.057
OPERATOR: <i>...an inmate at Robert</i>
Gordon Correctional Facility.

28:02.140 --> 28:04.768
<i>-Do you accept the charges?</i>
-Um, you guys,

28:04.852 --> 28:05.936
don't open the presents
without me.

28:06.019 --> 28:07.437
I'll be right back, okay?

28:13.485 --> 28:16.363
-Yes, I'll accept.
-KAI: <i>You fucking liar!</i>

28:16.446 --> 28:17.698
The only thing ever keeping you
alive was the fact that

28:17.781 --> 28:18.866
you were the mother of my child.

28:18.949 --> 28:20.200
Now you've got nothing!

28:21.159 --> 28:24.079
I take it you got a delivery
from Elite Genetics.

28:24.162 --> 28:26.415
(UNSTEADY CHUCKLE)

28:27.124 --> 28:28.792
<i>Now you can truly see</i>

28:28.876 --> 28:30.711
how over you are.

28:31.503 --> 28:33.714
Oz is not your son.

28:33.964 --> 28:35.632
<i>Your gang of circle-jerking</i>

28:35.716 --> 28:37.634
fascists are all dead,

28:37.718 --> 28:39.636
your brother and sister
are dead,

28:39.720 --> 28:41.388
<i>and you are trapped in a cage</i>

28:41.471 --> 28:43.473
<i>with nothing but other men.</i>

28:43.557 --> 28:47.394
Your sick, ugly, necrotic DNA

28:47.477 --> 28:50.898
will rot in prison
until you die.

28:53.066 --> 28:55.319
And then it will be gone
from the world forever.

28:55.402 --> 28:58.655
You think prison can stop me?
Prison is a fucking upgrade!

28:58.739 --> 29:00.532
<i>I'm building a real army</i>
<i>of real men.</i>

29:00.616 --> 29:01.909
<i>We are gonna get out,</i>

29:01.992 --> 29:03.827
and we are coming
straight for you.

29:03.911 --> 29:06.163
I am a goddamn movement!

29:06.246 --> 29:07.706
<i>I am coming for you!</i>

29:07.789 --> 29:10.667
<i>I am gonna rip you apart</i>
<i>piece by piece</i>

29:10.751 --> 29:11.877
<i>and make that son of a bitch</i>

29:11.960 --> 29:13.337
son of yours watch!

29:13.420 --> 29:14.463
You hear me, Ally?

29:14.546 --> 29:16.089
I am coming for you!

29:16.173 --> 29:18.008
You are a dead woman!

29:18.717 --> 29:20.219
-(PHONE CLANGING)
-(BEEP)

29:22.304 --> 29:24.681
Hey! That's government property.

29:32.481 --> 29:35.108
I'm ready to go back
to my cell now, Gloria.

29:35.275 --> 29:36.985
Yes, Divine Ruler.

29:44.201 --> 29:46.203
(MOANING)

29:50.332 --> 29:54.211
<i>After much reflection,</i>
<i>I realized I have a duty.</i>

29:54.294 --> 29:57.297
<i>I have survived,</i>
<i>I have overcome,</i>

29:57.381 --> 29:58.757
<i>and I want to harness</i>
<i>the strength</i>

29:58.841 --> 30:00.551
<i>I have gained to create hope</i>

30:00.634 --> 30:04.429
for our community,
hope for the future.

30:04.513 --> 30:06.849
Which is why I am here today

30:06.932 --> 30:08.934
<i>to announce my run</i>
<i>for the office</i>

30:09.017 --> 30:10.352
<i>of United States Senator</i>

30:10.435 --> 30:12.104
<i>from the great state</i>
<i>of Michigan.</i>

30:12.187 --> 30:13.605
-(APPLAUSE)
-(KAI GRUNTS)

30:13.939 --> 30:15.732
That's my Senate seat.

30:22.197 --> 30:25.993
All my life,
I have been told to smile,

30:26.076 --> 30:29.288
stay quiet, look pretty,

30:29.371 --> 30:31.540
not to stand out from the crowd.

30:32.541 --> 30:33.876
<i>And you know where that got me?</i>

30:34.960 --> 30:36.879
<i>Trapped in a cult,</i>

30:36.962 --> 30:38.922
<i>burying my wife,</i>

30:39.006 --> 30:41.758
<i>nearly losing my son, Oz.</i>

30:41.842 --> 30:45.220
<i>I was only able to break free</i>
<i>because I was finally unafraid</i>

30:45.304 --> 30:47.806
to separate from the pack.

30:47.890 --> 30:49.850
Well, now that I've escaped a cult,

30:49.933 --> 30:53.270
I'm running for Senate
to help you escape yours.

30:53.687 --> 30:57.566
It's time we band together
to bring down all cults...

30:57.649 --> 31:01.028
the Democratic party,
the Republican party,

31:01.111 --> 31:04.156
the entire two-party system.

31:04.239 --> 31:07.534
<i>I know what it looks like</i>
<i>when a powerful few</i>

31:07.618 --> 31:09.703
<i>control the many.</i>

31:09.786 --> 31:12.748
On Capitol Hill, they may not
want to listen to a woman

31:12.831 --> 31:16.168
who will take a sledgehammer
to their antiquated system of oppression,

31:16.877 --> 31:18.420
but with your support,

31:18.504 --> 31:20.923
they're not gonna have a choice.

31:22.674 --> 31:24.426
<i>I'm Ally Mayfair-Richards,</i>

31:24.510 --> 31:26.470
<i>and I approved this message.</i>

31:27.596 --> 31:30.432
BEVERLY: The focus group liked
the ad... they like you.

31:30.516 --> 31:34.019
You scored high marks across all
the favorability categories,

31:34.102 --> 31:35.354
and there's not a person
in this country

31:35.437 --> 31:36.688
that doesn't know your name

31:36.772 --> 31:38.065
and all the shit
you've been through.

31:38.148 --> 31:39.274
Then why am I still trailing
in the polls?

31:39.358 --> 31:40.776
People are rooting for you.

31:40.859 --> 31:42.402
They wanted us to know
they're on your side,

31:42.486 --> 31:43.904
especially the women.

31:43.987 --> 31:46.365
But when it came time
to rate you on strength,

31:46.448 --> 31:48.116
you came in at 25%.

31:48.200 --> 31:50.744
Only 14% trust you to lead,

31:50.827 --> 31:53.497
and they dinged you on
"lack of experience."

31:54.206 --> 31:56.041
Lack of experience?

31:57.209 --> 31:59.378
Code for they're scared.

31:59.795 --> 32:01.713
Isn't it sad when a strong woman

32:01.797 --> 32:04.049
scares people
more than clowns?

32:08.595 --> 32:11.473
What do people see
when they look at me?

32:12.432 --> 32:14.184
They see Kai.

32:16.270 --> 32:17.813
Well, look...

32:18.480 --> 32:21.066
we're not helping the situation
by putting him in the ad.

32:21.149 --> 32:22.693
Take him out.

32:23.026 --> 32:26.029
Put something out there with
just my picture alone.

32:26.113 --> 32:27.781
As long as he's alive,

32:27.865 --> 32:29.908
a picture of you <i>is</i>
a picture of Kai.

32:29.992 --> 32:32.077
-Oh...
-You're tied to him.

32:32.160 --> 32:34.705
You'll always be seen as his victim.

32:34.997 --> 32:36.623
Well...

32:36.915 --> 32:39.793
we just have to expand
people's imaginations.

32:40.043 --> 32:44.590
This debate with Senator Jackson,
this is your chance.

32:44.882 --> 32:46.842
He's gonna come at you hard.

32:46.925 --> 32:49.136
This is your only shot
for the public to see you

32:49.219 --> 32:51.096
take that motherfucker down.

32:51.180 --> 32:53.348
Then we better give them a show.

32:58.937 --> 33:01.940
(BREATHING DEEPLY)

33:02.024 --> 33:03.859
(EXHALING)

33:23.587 --> 33:24.671
Divine Ruler.

33:27.216 --> 33:28.217
It's perfect.

33:28.300 --> 33:30.219
Did you get the tattoos?

33:30.302 --> 33:31.553
Just like yours.

33:35.891 --> 33:37.809
I'm getting out of here, Rim Shot.

33:42.689 --> 33:44.316
Take me with you.

33:46.610 --> 33:47.903
Please.

33:48.529 --> 33:50.489
I won't make it
when you're gone.

33:52.074 --> 33:54.159
I-I can't make it without you!

33:58.497 --> 33:59.831
Believe me...

34:00.666 --> 34:01.875
I need you

34:01.959 --> 34:05.003
just as much as you need me.

34:05.629 --> 34:07.172
Tonight...

34:07.714 --> 34:09.216
we'll both be free.

34:09.299 --> 34:10.509
(STIFLED SOB)

34:11.510 --> 34:13.428
Thank you. (GRUNTS)

34:15.848 --> 34:17.766
(KAI EXHALES)

34:25.357 --> 34:27.109
Come on, we're on schedule.

34:28.735 --> 34:31.154
It was your idea
to cut off his face.

34:31.238 --> 34:32.906
Let's get to it.

34:32.990 --> 34:34.825
You clearly know your way
around the deli meats.

34:35.242 --> 34:37.452
I struggle with my food choices.

34:37.536 --> 34:40.831
Just help me mutilate the body
so he can be me.

34:54.136 --> 34:55.387
(LOCK BUZZES)

35:17.117 --> 35:19.077
(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)

35:20.287 --> 35:21.914
There's breaking news.

35:23.290 --> 35:25.334
Convicted murderer, Kai Anderson,

35:25.417 --> 35:27.544
was found dead this afternoon.

35:27.628 --> 35:30.506
Face mutilated beyond recognition.

35:33.592 --> 35:35.969
You sure you want
to go through with this?

35:38.639 --> 35:40.098
Do we have a choice?

35:41.225 --> 35:43.769
We've spent weeks
preparing for tonight.

35:45.521 --> 35:47.064
Let's do it.

35:50.275 --> 35:52.361
ALLY: Leadership is about two things:

35:52.444 --> 35:54.863
intelligence and independence.

35:55.113 --> 35:56.907
Facts and truth mean nothing

35:56.990 --> 35:59.368
if our leader is an idiot,

35:59.451 --> 36:01.370
or owned by special interests.

36:01.453 --> 36:03.330
What I can say about my opponent

36:03.413 --> 36:05.749
is he's not an idiot.

36:06.750 --> 36:08.335
(APPLAUSE, CHEERING)

36:09.795 --> 36:11.630
As most of you know,

36:11.713 --> 36:14.591
I have been through hell
these past two years.

36:14.967 --> 36:16.760
But so has our country.

36:16.844 --> 36:18.762
This idea that
America is a hellhole

36:18.846 --> 36:20.639
since the 2016 election

36:20.722 --> 36:22.474
is a creation
of a hysterical press...

36:22.558 --> 36:24.643
Would you do me a favor
and try not to interrupt me?

36:24.726 --> 36:26.270
You can't intimidate me,

36:26.353 --> 36:28.730
and I am tired
of being mansplained to.

36:28.814 --> 36:30.899
(APPLAUSE, WHOOPING)

36:30.983 --> 36:33.277
